It's too bad it violates the "safe area", the sprites are right down to the bottom of the screen, and will probably be clipped on old TVs.  New HDTVs don't clip, and instead refuse to display a progressive image.<br /><br />Edit: I meant on NTSC.  I hear PAL doesn't clip anything.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Thu Nov 10, 2011 10:12 pm</p><hr />
